t helper source in the same package. It might be a good idea to check if there are existing helpers in the library packages to streamline things. I wonder what those existing helpers might offer and if they could cover my needs without reinventing the wheel. By seeing what's available, I can make a more informed decision on how to proceed with the test setup!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_xzQkPXcMziX0yvWm7xlaOD31|fc_06f812db6eb55f6c016a007f29978c81a19e49461fd28c9e2d", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "find tests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java -type f | sort"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 659, "output": 993, "cacheRead": 68096, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 69748, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778417431503, "responseId": "resp_06f812db6eb55f6c016a007f1830a081a18ff203ba88b5f41e"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_xzQkPXcMziX0yvWm7xlaOD31|fc_06f812db6eb55f6c016a007f29978c81a19e49461fd28c9e2d", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "tests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/BasicAuthSchemeTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/CertAuthSchemeTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/DetailedCookieAssertionTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/ExplicitNoAuthSchemeTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/FormAuthSchemeTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/HeaderMatcherTest.java\ntests/src/io.rest-assured/rest-assured/5.5.0/src/test/java/io_rest_assured/rest_assured/NTLMAuthSchemeTest.java\ntests/src/io.r